#scriba
  [ title = The scriba manual
  ]

##section [ title = Introduction ]

&p This document will in time be expanded to a full discussion of the scriba
   markup language and library system. It's written in syntactically-valid
   scriba, with suggestive (but presently undefined) element names.

##section [ title = Syntax reference ]

&p Scriba, like other mixed-content markup languages, is a programming language
   with unmarked strings and marked commands.
